content:
Activate Work Summaries for Enhanced Messaging Sessions

To enable agents to generate and store messaging session summaries, activate work summaries for messaging sessions.

REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS
Edit (on Salesforce object) OR Modify All Data

From Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Einstein Work Summaries, then select Einstein Work Summaries.
Click the Enhanced Messaging tab.
To enable Work Summaries for enhanced messaging sessions, activate Messaging Session Summaries.
title: Activating Work Summaries in Service Cloud
